Free Trial Learn More 

 

"We deployed Intercept X to more than 5,000 endpoints. Since deploying, it has stopped 400 new ransomware attacks and we’ve had zero ransomware infections."










Intercept X


Free Trial Learn More 






Intercept X adds next-gen capabilities to your current endpoint protection.




Stops all forms of ransomware


Protection from advanced exploits


