Sophos Group PLC ADR


            
            Sophos Group Plc engages in the provision of cloud-enabled end user and network security solutions. The firm offers organizations integrated end-to-end protection against known and unknown information technology security threats. It operates through the following geographical segments: Europe; Middle East and Africa (EMEA); and The Americas and Asia Pacific and Japan. The company was founded on May 26, 2015 and is headquartered in Abingdon, United Kingdom.

            
            (See Full Profile)


  




